#inner-work[
  *The Lead Meditation*

  Obtain a small piece of lead (a fishing weight, a piece of lead sheet, or
  similar; available from fishing or hardware suppliers). Clean it and hold it
  in gloved hands for twenty minutes.

  Attend to its weight, its temperature, its dullness of surface. Notice
  what quality of awareness arises in your body and mind in the presence of
  this metal. After the session, wash hands thoroughly, remove and set aside
  the gloves, and record your impressions. What does lead feel like as a
  living planetary force?
]

